    <class name="Collector"
           c:symbol-prefix="collector"
           c:type="CloudProvidersCollector"
           parent="GObject.Object"
           glib:type-name="CloudProvidersCollector"
           glib:get-type="cloud_providers_collector_get_type"
           glib:type-struct="CollectorClass">
      <doc xml:space="preserve"
           filename="src/cloudproviderscollector.c"
           line="44">Singleton for tracking all providers.

This is a singleton to track all the changes in all providers.
Using this class, you can implement integration for all of them at once and represent them in the
UI, track new providers added or removed and their status.</doc>
